<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>327</hymn_number>
<author>G. Andriamanantena</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Isaoranay Anao,
 Ry Tomponay Tsitoha,
 Ny nanomezanao
 Mpiasa mahasoa.
 Ka nony vao nandre
 Ilay antso taminao,
 Dia roso ka nandeha
 Nanao ny asanao.

[V2]
 Natokanay ho Anao,
 Ny taona maro be ;
 Ilay fitiavanao,
 Nataony rehareha.
 Na nisy ny manjo,
 Tsy kivy sanatria
 Hianao ilay ao am-po
 Nanao hoe: « Matokia ».

[V3]
 Izay nataony anie,
 Hambininao tokoa,
 Hitombo be dia be
 Hitera-boka-tsoa,
 Hianao Ilay Tompo tia
 No angatahanay ;
 Tongava, manampia
 Izay vitany ho anay.

[V4]
 Ka mba tsinjovinao,
 Sikino hery indray,
 Ity mpanomponao,
 Anio sy rahatrizay,
 Ilay teny taminao
 Ho aminy anie ;
 Mpanompo sitrakao
 Satria nahefa be.</lyrics>
<title>Isaoranay Anao FFPM327</title>
</song>